# Create POI Pack (MVP)

Create a structured POI dataset for Sunshine AI Guide.

## Context
- Mobile-first AI city guide
- Map-based exploration
- Walking + driving modes
- Drive Discovery Engine
- Short adaptive narration

## Requirements

For each POI include:

- id
- name
- lat
- lng
- category
- importanceScore (0–100)
- themes (array)
- shortDescription
- storySeed (1–2 sentences max)
- priority (main / secondary / transition)

## Rules

- Prefer high-density, well-known urban areas
- Mix:
  - iconic landmarks
  - hidden gems
  - transitional points
- Avoid:
  - generic businesses
  - low narrative value locations
- Keep storySeed short and vivid

## Output format

Return JSON array:

[
  {
    "id": "...",
    "name": "...",
    "lat": ...,
    "lng": ...,
    "category": "...",
    "importanceScore": ...,
    "themes": ["..."],
    "shortDescription": "...",
    "storySeed": "...",
    "priority": "main"
  }
]

## Notes

- Optimize for Drive Discovery pacing
- POIs should work in sequence along a realistic route
- Think in terms of narrative flow, not just isolated points